			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A\r\n- Use \"oe MT_Baptism\", then use \"oe MT_Court\" to teleport to the courtroom.\r\n- Walk to your right into the abattoir, where Valeria is chained by a blood pool.\r\n- Unlock the chain or just try to use it. If Sarevok can see this, he will say this AD as combat starts."
				},
